        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
          Is my donation tax-deductible?
          <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-in">Yes. We are registered under Section 80G, so donations within India are eligible for tax deduction. You'll receive an emailed receipt immediately after payment that you can use for filing.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item rv">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
          How much of my donation actually reaches the cause?
          <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-in">72% goes directly to programs (meals, education, medicine). 16% covers logistics and distribution, and 12% covers core operations and staff. We publish this breakdown publicly — see our Transparency section above.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item rv">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
          Can I volunteer if I don't live in a city you operate in?
          <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-in">Yes — that's exactly how new chapters start. Use the "pin your city" tool on the Volunteer page, and our team will help you set up a chapter from scratch with a starter kit and mentor support.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item rv">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
          What payment methods do you accept?
          <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-in">Credit/debit cards, UPI, net banking, and wallets through Razorpay, plus direct UPI scan-and-pay if you prefer not to enter card details. International donors can pay via card in USD.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item rv">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
          Can I cancel a monthly donation anytime?
          <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-in">Yes, with no penalty. Manage or cancel your recurring donation anytime from your dashboard, or email us and we'll handle it within 24 hours.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


